// JSON Parser - Type Definitions
// ============================================================================
// Defines the core data structures for JSON parsing:
// - JsonValue: Represents any JSON value (null, bool, number, string, array, object)
// - ParseError: Error information with line/column tracking
// - Token: Lexical tokens used by the tokenizer
