## Break and Continue

### Break Early

```aria
loop(1, 100, 1) {
    if ($ > 50) {
        break;  // Exit loop when $ exceeds 50
    }
    print(`&{$}`);
}
// Prints: 1, 2, 3, ..., 50
```

### Skip Iterations

```aria
loop(1, 20, 1) {
    if ($ % 2 == 0) {
        continue;  // Skip even numbers
    }
    print(`Odd: &{$}`);
}
// Prints: 1, 3, 5, 7, ..., 19
```

---

## Nested Loops

### Shadow Behavior

```aria
// ⚠️ IMPORTANT: $ is shadowed in nested loops
loop(1, 3, 1) {
    int64:outer = $;  // Save outer $ value

    loop(1, 3, 1) {
        // Inner $ shadows outer $
        print(`Outer: &{outer}, Inner: &{$}`);
    }
```

### 2D Grid Iteration

```aria
// Iterate over 10x10 grid
loop(0, 9, 1) {
    int64:row = $;
    loop(0, 9, 1) {
        int64:col = $;
        processCell(row, col);
    }
```

