## Advanced Examples

### Example 1: Collatz Sequence

```aria
int64:n = 27;

while (n != 1) {
    print(`&{n}`);
    n = is (n % 2 == 0) : n / 2 : n * 3 + 1;
}

// Combined with loop:
loop(1, 100, 1) {
    int64:n = $;
    int64:steps = 0;

    while (n != 1) {
        n = is (n % 2 == 0) : n / 2 : n * 3 + 1;
        steps++;
