## Best Practices

### ✅ DO: Use for Short, Inline Logic

```aria
// Good: Simple transformation
int32[]:doubled = map(numbers, len, int32(int32:x) { pass(x * 2); })?;
```

### ✅ DO: Be Explicit with Types

```aria
// Good: Clear parameter and return types
