## Advanced Examples

### Example 1: Generic Swap Function

```aria
func:swapBytes = void(byte@:a, byte@:b, int64:size) {
    till(size - 1, 1) {
        byte:temp = a[$];
        a[$] = b[$];
        b[$] = temp;
    }
};

// Use for any type
int64:x = 10, y = 20;
swapBytes(@x as byte@, @y as byte@, sizeof(int64));
```

### Example 2: Reference Counting (Manual)

```aria
%STRUCT RefCounted {
    int64:refCount,
    byte@:data
}

