## Conversion and Interop

### double ↔ float

```aria
// double → float (precision loss)
double:d = 3.141592653589793;
float:f = d.to_float();  // 3.14159274... (loses ~8 digits)

// float → double (exact conversion)
float:f = 3.14159274;
