```

### double ↔ Deterministic Types

```aria
// double → tfp64 (loses determinism guarantee)
double:d = 1.5;
tfp64:t = tfp64.from_double(d);

// tfp64 → double (safe)
tfp64:deterministic = tfp64.from_string("1.5");
