## Implementation Details

### Structure (C Runtime)

```c
// From include/backend/runtime/tfp_ops.h

struct Tfp32 {
    int16_t exp;      // TBB16 exponent (biased by 16383)
    int16_t mant;     // TBB16 mantissa (signed, 2's complement)
};

