## Determinism Guarantee

### The Promise

**tfp32/tfp64 guarantee**:
```
SAME INPUTS + SAME OPERATIONS = SAME BITS (everywhere, always)
```

**IEEE 754 reality**:
```
SAME INPUTS + SAME OPERATIONS = maybe same, maybe different (¯\_(ツ)_/¯)
```

