## Vector Operations

### Dot Product (9D Coherence)

The **dot product** in 9D measures **consciousness state alignment** (coherence):

```aria
vec9:state_now = vec9(0.5, 0.6, 0.7, 0.5, 0.3, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.5);
